  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread the sausages onto skewers, leaving a small space between each sausage.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the olive oil, chopped onion, minced garlic, tomato paste, beef broth, red wine, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the sausages, making sure they are fully coated.",
    "Grill the skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, until the sausages are browned and cooked through.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve the skewers hot, garnished with fresh parsley or oregano.",
    "Offer crusty bread or grilled vegetables on the side, if desired."
  ],
